        <p>
            This dialog lists all loadable plugins and allows you to enable/disable them.
        </p>

        <list>
            <title>The "Loaded Plugins:" table offers the following columns:</title>
            <item><p>Enabled - Check or uncheck this field if to enable or disable the respective plugin. If it offers a further configuration dialog, it will appear appear below the "Plugins:" menu point in GMPC's Preferences window.</p></item>
            <item><p>Name - The name of the plugin</p></item>
            <item><p>Function - What type of enhancement does the plugin provide</p></item>
            <item><p>Version - The version number of the plugin.</p></item>
        </list>
</page>
